boat.full_description:
LizAnna is a Bay Cruiser 23 built by Swallow Yachts in 2013. Her owner put a deposit down at the Southampton Boat Show in 2012 and took possession directly after the boat show in 2013. LizAnna was the first BC23 to have an inboard engine fitted and was exhibited on their stand at the 2013 show.

She has been sailed in the Poole and Solent areas.
